<Math equation-number="6.8.1" mode="display" xml:id="C6.S8.E1">\frac{1}{2}\ln\left(1+\frac{2}{x}\right)&lt;e^{x}E_{1}\left(x\right)&lt;\ln\left(1+ \frac{1}{x}\right),</Math> <Math equation-number="6.8.2" mode="display" xml:id="C6.S8.E2">\frac{x}{x+1}&lt;xe^{x}E_{1}\left(x\right)&lt;\frac{x+1}{x+2},</Math> <Math equation-number="6.8.3" mode="display" xml:id="C6.S8.E3">\frac{x(x+3)}{x^{2}+4x+2}&lt;xe^{x}E_{1}\left(x\right)&lt;\frac{x^{2}+5x+2}{x^{2}+6x +6}</Math>.
</sentence>

